The paper focuses on automated categorization and extraction of scientific concepts from titles of scientific articles, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories in computer science, such as computational linguistics (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and deep learning (cs.DL). Among these, cs.CL and cs.IR are the most likely sub-categories as they directly relate to the paper's focus on natural language processing and information retrieval.
